Resource Profile: Radiation Dose Observation

Official URL: http://hl7.eu/fhir/imaging-r5/StructureDefinition/ImRadiationDoseObservation Version: 0.1.0-ballot
Standards status: Draft Maturity Level: 1 Computable Name: ImRadiationDoseObservation

Copyright/Legal: Used by permission of HL7 Europe, all rights reserved Creative Commons License

A record for the radiation dose the subject has been exposed to during an imaging procedure. E.g. based on information from https://dicom.nema.org/medical/dicom/current/output/html/part16.html and https://build.fhir.org/ig/HL7/fhir-radiation-dose-summary-ig/index.html

Usages:

  • Derived from this Profile: Report obligations for ImRadiationDoseObservation
